                      "parameters":  {
                                         "color":  4,
                                         "width":  560,
                                         "height":  220,
                                         "content":  "### Cloud-safe Telegram Router\n- No Telegram credentials required in nodes.\n- Uses webhook + Telegram Bot API HTTP calls.\n- Set env vars in n8n: TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN, SCBE_BRIDGE_URL, SCBE_API_KEY.\n- Set BotFather webhook to: https://\u003cyour-n8n-domain\u003e/webhook/telegram-clayofsand"
                                     }
                  }
